snippet.title: Welcome to The Arcade!
snippet.description:
Get early access! 
https://www.portalone.com/playtime

Discover a brand new mobile gaming entertainment experience... where everyone has a chance to win real prizes! 

Be one of the first to ever play in the PortalOne Arcade. 

Get invitation-only access to our limited private beta. The beta test opens in Norway first (June 2020) and will be available in additional countries after that.
